    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208030/extras/7fc950c7df5589470036169b1582e4ba.poster.avif?t=1757950853\" aria-label=\"A two-sections banner. The section to the right contains the word &quot;DEMO&quot; in bold black and white letters in a chequered moving blue background. The Section to the right contains an artwork of the character Pip standing Idle in the demo park level.\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208030/extras/7fc950c7df5589470036169b1582e4ba.webm?t=1757950853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pip Pepper Park Planner</strong> is an <i>upcoming </i> <i>cozy</i> + thinky<i> </i>game in which you play as <strong>Pip</strong>, a <i>little </i>bird with a <i>big</i> job: to design parks for animals to enjoy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Explore different habitats, discover the needs of diverse animals and fully customize your parks. Can you build a park that all the animals will love?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208030/extras/e0d2e6d23ea96f25ecb8db711358f465.poster.avif?t=1757950853\" aria-label=\"In-game footage of Pip, a bird with a construction helmet, standing idle with a bouncy animation in the game world.\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208030/extras/e0d2e6d23ea96f25ecb8db711358f465.webm?t=1757950853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEMO FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 customizable park areas in the demo level. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > +300 possible combinations to try with multiple endings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 diverse animal groups full of personality.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > +120 unique and fun dialogue lines.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONTROLS:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game controls appear on-screen. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepads are supported and recommended. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
